/**
 * Service
 */
public class TestService {
  private String message;

  public String getMessage() {
    return message;
  }

  public void setMessage(String message) {
    this.message = message;
  }

  public String sayMessage(){
    return message;
  }
}
```

# AutoConfigure
----

```java
/**
 * TestServiceProprtiesTestService
 */
@Configuration                                                                                                                              
@EnableConfigurationProperties(value = TestServiceProperties.class)                                                                        
@ConditionalOnClass(TestService.class)                                                                                                     
@ConditionalOnProperty(prefix = "test", value = "enable", matchIfMissing = true)  
public class TestAutoConfiguration {

  @Autowired                                                                                                                              
  private TestServiceProperties testServiceProperteis;                                                                                  

  @Bean                                                                                                                                   
  @ConditionalOnMissingBean(TestService.class)                                                                                           
  public TestService testService() {                                                                                                    
    TestService testService = new TestService();                                                                                     
    testService.setMessage(testServiceProperteis.getMessage());                                                                               
    return testService;                                                                                                                
  }                     
}
```

- ** @Configurationspring **

- ** @EnableConfigurationProperties(value = TestServiceProperties.class):valuevalue={xxProperties1.class,xxProperteis2.class....} **

- ** @ConditionalOnClass(TestService.class):classPathTestService.class **

- ** @ConditionalOnProperty(prefix = "test", value = "enable", matchIfMissing = true):testenableenable **

